title: Hojo Mojo With Chojo (Live) 320cbr (Big Papi) 2003 Blues
description:
Source:  2003 CD
 
[i]This is a live performance so the gaps between tracks were removed so audience clapping and songs continue seamlessly.  There are a couple of tracks where the studio cut parts of the performance out so the gaps serve no purpose then.   The band has a real down home feel and the musicians are highly skilled.  The genre is blues but it has a very country feel.  - Big Papi[/i]
